reviews.customers_say: Customers love the sweater's heart elbow patches and find it comfortable, not itchy, and loose in all the right places.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars This products is absolutely FANTASTIC!
items.body: I just wore this for Valentines Day when we went out to Dinner and was complimented by several people. The color is very vibrant and the hearts fit perfectly where they are supposed to. The sweater is very soft and comfortable. Not too hot or too cool, actually the perfect weight! I wore with black leggings so the length is long enough to do that or you could wear jeans. Pick this sweater up, it is adorable! Read more

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good purchase
items.body: It’s super cute!! I was a little disappointed in the front being so plain but the patches on the sleeves are what caught my eye. Fits true to size. Not too heavy but still very warm. Read more
items.author: Jeff & Dayna

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute and so comfortable!
items.body: I have been one in the sweater for a long time.... However, I am a shopping addict. And I don't need a new sweater! I finally caught it on sale and I couldn't be happier. I wish I would have purchased add a long time ago. It is so comfortable. It fits great and I got a lot of compliments on it. It is not too heavy or to light. I will definitely as a trying to be recovered shopping addict. Be looking for another sale for the sweater and purchase more! Read more
items.author: BRITTANY

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Poorly made but cute and comfortable
items.body: As soon as I open the package I could tell that the scenes were not held together while the sleeves and the bottom of the shirt so in order to keep it from saying and falling apart I went in and hand stitched all of the seams together better. Really shouldn’t have to do that I should be able to wear the sweater confidently and not see that other bag but the sleeves are already coming apart. I haven’t watched it yet but I am a little fearful it will fall apart in the washer and hoping my reinforcing the stitches will help that. It is a very cute design and it fits very well and it’s very soft so I wish it was made better quality and I didn’t have to fix it before wearing it. Read more
items.author: Liz s

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adorable!
items.body: I love this adorable sweater!! The heart elbows are so cute and the sweater has an overall flattering, looser fit. The material isn't too thin and is not translucent knitting. Read more
items.author: Stuart

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Really long sleeves
items.body: I’m so disappointed because I love this sweater but the sleeves almost cover my entire hand and the cuff isn’t fitted enough to keep them up. I ordered the red, great color, soft fabric, cute details but freakish long sleeves so sadly I’m going to return it. I’m 5’4 - 160lbs & I have normal arms. I ordered a large & everything else is great. Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: A Thick Navy, B Red, T-khaki, A Thick Camel, T-pink, A Thick Dark Grey, B Black, T-black, B Camel, G-80 White, A Thin Grey, B Grey, T-grey, A Thick Wine-red. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
